snippet.title: Hello Neighbor 2 - AI Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
Play as a local journalist in the familiar Raven Brooks in Hello Neighbor 2. The AI for Mr. Peterson constantly changes over time as the community plays Hello Neighbor 2. However, in Hello Neighbor 2, even more NPCs can be interacted with and changed.

#SummerOfGaming
